0],"flags":{},"order":6,"mode":0,"inputs":[],"outputs":[],"properties":{},"widgets_values":["\n## 作者/Author\n黎黎原上咩（SweetValberry）\n\n\n## 视频教程/Video Tutorial\n\n\nB站视频教程：https://www.bilibili.com/video/BV1AABYYvE2H/"],"color":"#ffffff","bgcolor":"#ffffff"},{"id":5,"type":"ShowText|pysssss","pos":[3650,3270],"size":[480,410],"flags":{},"order":19,"mode":0,"inputs":[{"label":"text","localized_name":"text","name":"text","type":"STRING","link":1}],"outputs":[{"label":"STRING","localized_name":"字符串","name":"STRING","shape":6,"type":"STRING","links":null}],"properties":{"cnr_id":"comfyui-custom-scripts","ver":"1.2.5","Node name for S&R":"ShowText|pysssss"},"widgets_values":["In a dimly lit, neon-drenched alleyway, a young woman stands out amidst the gritty backdrop in a tattered, red-leather corset adorned with holographic circuitry and flickering blue LEDs. The air is thick with the hum of machinery and the distant thrum of basslines.\n\nHer hair is styled into a messy, cybernetic mohawk, complete with glowing blue stripes and embedded micro-servos that twitch and flex as she moves. A pair of mirrored shades perched on her forehead reflect the neon glow of the alleyway, while a chunky, silver arm cuff wraps around her wrist, pulsing with an soft blue light.\n\nA delicate, circuit-patterned tattoo on her left cheekbone glows softly in sync with the beat of the music, as if it's alive. The woman's eyes gleam with a mix of determination and recklessness, set against the stark, high-tech backdrop of the city's underbelly."]},{"id":32,"type":"Note","pos":[3380,3350],"size":[230,88],"flags":{},"order":8,"mode":0,"inputs":[],"outputs":[],"properties":{},"widgets_values":["这里建议使用擅长文字处理的大语言模型，例如：llama3.1:8b"],"color":"#ffffff","bgcolor":"#ffffff"},{"id":33,"type":"Note","pos":[1580,3030],"size":[260,88],"flags":{},"order":7,"mode":0,"inputs":[],"outputs":[],"properties":{},"widgets_values":["这里需要使用视觉大语言模型，例如：minicpm-v:8b"],"color":"#ffffff","bgcolor":"#ffffff"},{"id":22,"type":"Ol